- How we implement methods from Button ? Do we have to implemnt them in the decorator, or can we call them on getInstance, or apple avant passer param
- extends or decorator

extend
avantage :
 - herite de toutes les methodes
desavantage :
- doit extend tous les types

decorator
- pas besoin d'extend tous les types
- doit reimplementer toutes les methodes

A method called public void step() that iterates through the cells of the
array changing the state of the world by updating the position of all the
Autonomous and Moveable objects (see below). It does this once for each call to
the method.

A public void step() method that randomly picks a direction and updates
the item to a new location by one cell.
